tip.text: Iconic London. A must visit for every visitor to this city.
A good way to spend the morning or afternoon,  out of the busy tourist area of the old town. Wonderful atmosphere.
The goulash is awesome. But their food in general is really good. Recommended restaurant. Reserve in advance though.
In the ferry ride to the saint bartholomew island, sit on the right side of the boat so you can photograph the church. Do the reverse on the ride back to the entrance.
Great place to eat in Marienplatz. Family friendly.
